    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完蛋！坤坤不堪被小黑子羞辱，转而向牢大学习篮球技术，而牢大的考验是必须寻找会爆炸的篮球。 <br>坤坤轮盘是Rougelite+万宁版的恶魔轮盘，更爽更刺激。  <br>拥有各种场外援助技能扭转战局（包括和牢大互换道具，逆转所有实弹和空弹的强力援助技能）  <br>可以构建各种build，让坤坤能获得更高的篮球技术。  <br>获得的金钱不只是数字，可以通过练习两年半不断提升坤坤的篮球技术，直到超越牢大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全成就大约2.5个小时，多人模式正在开发中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BUG反馈+讨论群：780667330</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021000/extras/118f31cdf0f45f43cb2538e21b5c2ca8.poster.avif?t=1769951807\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021000/extras/118f31cdf0f45f43cb2538e21b5c2ca8.webm?t=1769951807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021000/extras/118f31cdf0f45f43cb2538e21b5c2ca8.mp4?t=1769951807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入篮球场，与牢大撅战，要么炸飞牢大，要么坤坤爆炸。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择会爆炸的篮球砸向牢大，选择不会爆炸的篮球砸向自己。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同于充斥着恐怖气息的恶魔轮盘，无论输赢都会让你会心一笑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着回合数增长而不断使出真本领的牢大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021000/extras/be86a43fcd0611a9c74074a22c686452.avif?t=1769951807\" width=1530 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
